OL,3,CFormer prison officer had no intention
OL,4,Cof stirring up social media hate
OL,6,FA former prison officer has told a
OL,7,Fjury he did not intend to stir up
OL,8,Fracial hatred on social media in the
OL,9,Fwake of the Southport attacks.
OL,11,FMark Heath, who's 45-years-old, is
OL,12,Faccused of stirring up racial hatred
OL,13,Fon X by publishing allegedly
OL,14,Fthreatening, abusive or insulting
OL,15,Fmaterial to the site between 22 July
OL,16,Fand 6 August this year.
OL,18,FHeath, a father-of-one, of Kestrel
OL,19,FRoad in Oakham, is a former car sales
OL,20,Fmanager and prison officer at HMP
OL,21,FPeterborough.
