OL,3,CFormer prison officer had no intention
OL,4,Cof stirring up social media hate
OL,6,FProsecutors allege he posted "talk of
OL,7,Fwar" and images that targeted people
OL,8,Fon the grounds of their race,
OL,9,Fincluding a claim that Islam is a
OL,10,F"common problem" for the world.
OL,12,F"I am not guilty"
OL,14,FGiving evidence to Leicester Crown
OL,15,FCourt, sitting at Loughborough
OL,16,FCourthouse, Heath said he regretted
OL,17,Fpart of a post in which he described
OL,18,FMuslim men being involved in an
OL,19,Fincident at Manchester Airport as
OL,20,Fbeing a "Brucey bonus."
