OL,3,CFormer prison officer had no intention
OL,4,Cof stirring up social media hate
OL,6,FHe told jurors nothing he had every
OL,7,Fposted on X - which he viewed as a
OL,8,F'safe space' for freedom of speech
OL,9,Fafter its takeover by Elon Musk - was
OL,10,Fintended to stir up hatred.
OL,12,FHe said: "I pleaded guilty because I
OL,13,Fam not guilty.
OL,15,F"I do have strong opinions and express
OL,16,Fthose opinions but at no point was I
OL,17,Ftrying to stir up racial hatred or did
OL,18,FI think that it was likely to stir
OL,19,Fanything up.
