OL,3,CFormer prison officer had no intention
OL,4,Cof stirring up social media hate
OL,6,F"I am very much right wing. I do not
OL,7,Fhate all Muslims... but I do have
OL,8,Fmajor issues with radical Islam."
OL,10,FCommenting on an incident in which a
OL,11,Fman was kicked in the head by police
OL,12,Fat Manchester airport, Heath posted on
OL,13,F25 July: "You know what it doesn't
OL,14,Fmatter what religion, colour etc the
OL,15,Fpeople involved were, an English man
OL,16,Fwould have deserved the same treatment!
OL,18,F"The fact it turned out to be a group
OL,19,Fof Muslim men was a Brucey bonus!"
