OL,6,FHeath told jurors: "I do regret
OL,7,Fputting the last bit I must admit. It
OL,8,Fwas a silly thing to say.
OL,10,F"Having said that I do perceive those
OL,11,FMuslims to be radical because anybody
OL,12,Fthat is up for attacking a group of
OL,13,Farmed police officers, in my eyes, is
OL,14,Fpretty radical."
OL,16,FA Reform Party logo on the front of a
OL,17,Ftrain was his main X account picture,
OL,18,FHeath said, telling the court: "I
OL,19,Fagree with their policies and what
OL,20,Fthey would do if they were to govern
OL,21,Fat any point."
